            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Volcano <lb n="2"/>aram <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ors</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>Bitur</abbr><ex>igum</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>uitata</ex></expan> <expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">cu</supplied>r</abbr><ex>avit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden verbaut in der Quermauer eines Hauses, wohl aus Rottweil verschleppt. Kleiner Altar, beschädigt, unterer Teil des Inschriftfeldes frei geblieben.</p>
            </div>
